<plot>Hosted by storyteller Paul Douglas, this summer series started each episode with Douglas holding some artifact from England, which he would then use as the basis for a long, involved tale of adventure explaining how the object came to be in his possession. The show was brought back in repeats for its second summer season in 1957.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?024116</url></doc>
